  "prompt": "Where can I get my Hyosung Aquila GV250 (Carb) serviced in Bangalore? Anybody with experience in getting spares, reliable service centre, mechanic?",
  "response": "Finding a reliable service center and mechanic for your Hyosung Aquila GV250 (Carb) in Bangalore can be a bit challenging, but here are some places and suggestions to get you started:\n\n---\n\n### **Hyosung Authorized Service Centers**\nHyosung motorcycles are now sold and serviced by DSK Motowheels in India. You can contact their authorized service centers in Bangalore for genuine parts and reliable servicing.\n\n1. **DSK Motowheels Service Center**  \n   - Location: DSK Motowheels, Bangalore  \n   - Contact: Check their official website or call customer care for the nearest location.  \n   - They should have access to original spares and trained mechanics for Hyosung bikes.\n\n---\n\n### **Independent Mechanics with Hyosung Experience**\nIf you prefer independent mechanics, here are a few options:\n\n1. **Khan's Garage**  \n   - Location: Koramangala  \n   - Known for handling sport bikes and cruisers. They may have experience with Hyosung Aquila GV250.  \n   - Contact: Search online for their current details.\n\n2. **Rigid Choppers**  \n   - Location: Nagarbhavi  \n   - Specializes in cruisers and custom bikes. They might be able to help with servicing and spares for the Aquila GV250.  \n   - Contact: Search online for their current contact information.\n\n3. **Bike Works**  \n   - Location: Indiranagar  \n   - Popular for servicing and repairing a wide range of bikes, including cruisers.  \n   - Contact: Look them up online for recent details.\n\n---\n\n### **Spare Parts**  \nSpare parts for the Hyosung Aquila GV250 (Carb) can be tricky to find, but here\u2019s what you can do:  \n   - **DSK Motowheels**: Always the first choice for genuine spares.  \n   - **Local Dealers**: Check with motorcycle parts dealers in JC Road or other auto parts hubs in Bangalore.  \n   - **Online Platforms**: Websites like eBay, BikerZone, or IndiaMART may have spares for Hyosung Aquila GV250.\n\n---\n\n### **Tips for Reliable Service**  \n1. Always ask for the mechanic\u2019s experience with Hyosung bikes before handing over your bike.  \n2. Use genuine or high-quality aftermarket spares for better performance.  \n3. Check reviews or ask fellow riders for recommendations before choosing a service center.\n\nLet me know if you need further assistance!",
